    <entry>
      <title>解决hexo博客图片等文件无法上传的问题</title>
      <link href="2021/05/23/hexo-file-asset/"/>
      <url>2021/05/23/hexo-file-asset/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="安装插件"><a href="#安装插件" class="headerlink" title="安装插件"></a>安装插件</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-asset-image --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="出现异常，代表没有权限"><a href="#出现异常，代表没有权限" class="headerlink" title="出现异常，代表没有权限"></a>出现异常，代表没有权限</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm ERR! command failed</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR! command git --no-replace-objects ls-remote ssh://git@github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-asset-image.git</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR! key_load_public: invalid format</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR! git@github.com: Permission denied (publickey).</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR! fatal: Could not read from remote repository.</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR!</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR! Please make sure you have the correct access rights</span><br><span class="line">npm ERR! and the repository exists.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="验证邮箱和github注册邮箱输入的是否一致"><a href="#验证邮箱和github注册邮箱输入的是否一致" class="headerlink" title="验证邮箱和github注册邮箱输入的是否一致"></a>验证邮箱和github注册邮箱输入的是否一致</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global --list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="换上你自己的邮箱"><a href="#换上你自己的邮箱" class="headerlink" title="换上你自己的邮箱"></a>换上你自己的邮箱</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “这里换上你的邮箱”</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> hexo搭建 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>使用Hexo和githubpage发布博客</title>
      <link href="2021/05/23/post-title/"/>
      <url>2021/05/23/post-title/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="生成一个新的页面"><a href="#生成一个新的页面" class="headerlink" title="生成一个新的页面"></a>生成一个新的页面</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="部署文件"><a href="#部署文件" class="headerlink" title="部署文件"></a>部署文件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="上传文件到github"><a href="#上传文件到github" class="headerlink" title="上传文件到github"></a>上传文件到github</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo d  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="本地启动博客服务"><a href="#本地启动博客服务" class="headerlink" title="本地启动博客服务"></a>本地启动博客服务</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo s  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="监控文件变动服务能实时的更新页面"><a href="#监控文件变动服务能实时的更新页面" class="headerlink" title="监控文件变动服务能实时的更新页面"></a>监控文件变动服务能实时的更新页面</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g -w  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="发布草稿-用处不是很大"><a href="#发布草稿-用处不是很大" class="headerlink" title="发布草稿 用处不是很大"></a>发布草稿 用处不是很大</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo  publish  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查看hexo版本号"><a href="#查看hexo版本号" class="headerlink" title="查看hexo版本号"></a>查看hexo版本号</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo  version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="debug模式，将调试信息放到debug-log中"><a href="#debug模式，将调试信息放到debug-log中" class="headerlink" title="debug模式，将调试信息放到debug.log中"></a>debug模式，将调试信息放到debug.log中</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo  --debug</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="部署"><a href="#部署" class="headerlink" title="部署"></a>部署</h2><h3 id="安装hexo-deployer-git"><a href="#安装hexo-deployer-git" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo-deployer-git"></a>安装hexo-deployer-git</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查看安装是否成功"><a href="#查看安装是否成功" class="headerlink" title="查看安装是否成功"></a>查看安装是否成功</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm list hexo-deployer-git </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="deploy到github上-在config-yml文件下修改"><a href="#deploy到github上-在config-yml文件下修改" class="headerlink" title="deploy到github上 在config.yml文件下修改"></a>deploy到github上 在config.yml文件下修改</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/yishengyuan/blog.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">test</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装hexo-admin-插件"><a href="#安装hexo-admin-插件" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo-admin 插件"></a>安装hexo-admin 插件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-admin --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="hexo-admin-账号密码cookie"><a href="#hexo-admin-账号密码cookie" class="headerlink" title="hexo-admin 账号密码cookie"></a>hexo-admin 账号密码cookie</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">admin:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">username:</span> <span class="string">admin</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">password_hash:</span> <span class="number">123456</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">secret:</span> <span class="number">123456</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
